{
  "stem": "21349.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When we came to the port, was a small ship, 1,400 tons-- pretty ship-- and a ferry boat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were all searched.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father was searched more than we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we went down there and we went out and we left Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, we went first on the Elbe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Hamburg is also a little bit inside the river Elbe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we come to a point where the Elbe flows into the North Sea, the German Sea they call it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Cuxhaven is the name of that place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then we went a little bit further.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There is an island, Heligoland, which was bombed during the war and submerged, and afterwards Germany brought it up again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Up to that point, everything went fine and well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But then afterwards, I got very seasick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And and we came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We went on and we traveled-- instead of traveling 36 hours-- for the 24 hours it was 36 hours.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we landed then finally Friday morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I think we left Wednesday evening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We landed at-- on Friday morning 9:00 or 10 o'clock in a little village in England called Grimsby, G-R-I-M-S-B-Y.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That's a bay in the center of Britain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we only were allowed to take $4 out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Each one was only allowed $4.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that was signed in the book, in the-- in the passport and all over, $4 no more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And $4 at that time was 10 Reichsmark, 10 mark.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "At that time the mark was $2.50.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Don't forget, $1 was $2.50.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I took-- I think I took a haircut.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "From there, we were received by a man from-- by a company, Cunard-White Star.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they bought us by train, very quick train, from Grimsby to London.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And in London, they had a bus.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
